Each year on 16 June, people across the world celebrate the decadent and simple “caramel” treat otherwise known as fudge. To celebrate International Fudge Day, recreate and indulge in this sweet and savory bacon and banana fudge recipe. Make a larger batch of this delicious recipe so you can gift your loved ones with some fudge to further celebrate International Fudge Day. ALSO READ: The perfect nutty fudge recipe to celebrate National Nutty Fudge Day This recipe was supplied by Capsicum Culinary Studio